    A changelog for the site and projects — not a blog. Entries are short:
    "updated the dungeon lighting," "new pastel piece up." Updated when
    there's something to say.
  </p>
  <p class="dim">
    <span class="prompt"></span>log entries become a content collection in
    phase 2.
  </p>
</Base>
